  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK631">
<l>karuviyuṅ kālamuñ ceykaiyuñ ceyyu</l>
<l>maruviṉaiyu māṇṭa tamaiccu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The minister is one who can make an excellent choice of means, time, manner of execution, and the difficult undertaking (itself).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
